race.comment: BANNERED (6) led and just failed to hold on when resuming over this course and distance two back. Disappointed in town last time after working hard but failing to find the lead. Gets a few gear changes today and looks well placed after the claim. Should bounce back. REMINISCENCE (9) is a first starter by Farnan from Sylpheed who recorded multiple top three finishes at black-type level. Has trialled once since arriving in the Williams yard and caught the eye. Any money flow should be greatly respected. VIVA MARCONI (1) commenced awkwardly and never really got involved last time out over 1300m at this track. Better placed back to six furlongs so deserves another chance. DAKINED (7) passed a few when resuming over 1000m at Bunbury recently. Sneaky top three contender over an extra 200m out of gate one. LIKES TO CHANT (11) strips fitter second-up and is worth including in exotics.
